{"tid":949192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗大規模掃黃拘100人 包括16歲內地女","createTime":"2018-12-20T15:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T02:59:20.000Z","uid":42393,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f0b71355ae5abeacc60fe6396be5d1ad5969a5","tid":949192,"uid":42393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"元朗警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處人員一連9日（本月12日至20日）展開大規模掃黃行動，突擊搜查及掃蕩谷亭街、青山公路元朗段、同樂街、元朗安樂路、元朗炮仗坊、康景街、教育路、壽富街、福康街、福德街和豐年路一帶多個單位，共拘捕100名年齡介乎16至50歲內地女子涉嫌違反逗留條件，其中一名39歲女子同時涉嫌管理賣淫場所，另外10名年齡介乎16至50歲女子則同時涉嫌為不道德目的而唆使他人。<br />\n<br />\n行動中，人員檢獲安全套、潤滑劑、衣物及宣傳招牌等。所有被捕女子分別已被檢控或交由入境事務處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n16歲真係講緊讀中五<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4077da4741ad7a5e92d2826f2f217216602c3dda","tid":949192,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"16歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba28344880cf17f7afefceebbab2f475fd43b986","tid":949192,"uid":28765,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i407.photobucket.com/albums/pp157/LALALOVE_TW/ef033646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi407.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fpp157%2FLALALOVE_TW%2Fef033646.jpg&h=4eda3b99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dcd68d317fb24381a75143aed3d24c30b6c2ca0","tid":949192,"uid":42393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:33:36.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n報紙講埋邊度掃<br />\n<br />\n即係教你點幫櫬"},{"pid":"25b8882091f1c2194aa8cbdbdea474f77eabe639","tid":949192,"uid":17032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"年度最佳廣告"},{"pid":"cebe17af51835ecf09d0475c3a1ac375c9118e09","tid":949192,"uid":86097,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c039472542f52786cc33